{"ID":"20250707172644-ja7dmht","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20250707172644-ja7dmht","title":"MAC-VO: Metrics-aware Covariance for Learning-basedStereo Visual Odometry","type":"doc","updated":"20250711193643"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250708105330-ozwx3xg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20250708105330-ozwx3xg","updated":"20250711193643"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"摘要"}]},{"ID":"20250707172644-ubtkaly","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250707172644-ubtkaly","updated":"20250708105349"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一种基于学习的立体视觉里程计框架。该框架训练了一个度量感知不确定性模型"}]},{"ID":"20250708105258-dphipx7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250708105258-dphipx7","updated":"20250708110131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"功能1:在姿态图优化中选择关键点，对残差进行加权。传统几何方法倾向于选择边缘等纹理丰富的特征作为关键点。该模型基于全局不一致性提出低质量特征点。与基于学习的方法依赖与尺度无关性不同。提出的度量感知协方差模型，从学习到不确定性中推导出关键点配准中呃空间误差和轴间相关性，将协方差模型嵌入到姿态图优化中，MACVO在姿态估计方面实现了卓越的鲁棒性和准确性。"}]},{"ID":"20250708161238-23b7b1r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250708161238-23b7b1r","updated":"20250709175054"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"创新点1:"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 提出一个基于学习的模型量化2D度量感知不确定性。受FLowFormer 和GMA 的启发。采用迭代更新模型和运动聚合器来预测2d图像中不确定性。"}]},{"ID":"20250708182100-qt9jj28","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250708182100-qt9jj28","updated":"20250711193643"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"创新点2: "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"基于学习到的2D不确定值，使用度量感知3D协方差模型对3D空间中的特征点的协方差进行建模。相比于使用对角协方差矩阵，（Diagonal Covariance Matrix）其非对角元素全为0，对角元素上非零。意味着矩阵中的变量之间没有协方差，即不相关，只有每个变量自身的方差存在。"}]},{"ID":"20250709150505-z4f0uzs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250709150505-z4f0uzs","updated":"20250709150522"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提出的主要贡献："}]},{"ID":"20250709150523-2mtlbb8","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250709150523-2mtlbb8","updated":"20250709150530"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250709150530-aaz2wfx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250709150530-aaz2wfx","updated":"20250709150530"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250709150530-fjzign0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250709150530-fjzign0","updated":"20250709150647"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提出了一种基于学习且具有度量感知能力的二维不确定性网络，该网络利用迭代运动聚合器捕捉特征匹配的不一致性。使用这种度量感知不确定性来评估特征质量。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250709150648-7cf8uv1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250709150648-7cf8uv1","updated":"20250709150648"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250709150648-3v3fiby","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250709150648-3v3fiby","updated":"20250709150749"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"介绍了一种基于特征匹配和深度估计的二维不确定性的新型度量感知三维协方差模型。消融实验表明尺度一致性和位姿图优化中非对角项的必要性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250709150750-lbgsl29","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20250709150750-lbgsl29","updated":"20250709150750"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250709150750-fo4pnq4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250709150750-fo4pnq4","updated":"20250709150840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提出MACVO，双目视觉里程计，通过度量感知协方差来估计相机位姿，同时注册3D特征。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250709151545-emmlrqd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250709151545-emmlrqd","updated":"20250709151820"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"mark","TextMarkTextContent":"利用了一些原理：不确定性传播原理"}]},{"ID":"20250709151605-megixax","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250709151605-megixax","updated":"20250711193543"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在视觉SLAM中3D点是通过双目匹配或多视图集合从2d观测点三角化的来。根据误差传播定律，2D观测的协方差通过三角化函数传播到3D空间中"}]},{"ID":"20250709151759-2ahem9n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250709151759-2ahem9n","updated":"20250709180532"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相比于传统方法中简化为对角协方差矩阵，（假设各个方向上是独立的），而"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMa